"The packet transfers to the virtual NIC of the compute host, such as, vnet1."
" You can find out what vent NIC is being used by looking at the "
"/etc/libvirt/qemu/instance-xxxxxxxx.xml file."
msgstr ""

#: ./doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/ch_ops_network_troubleshooting.xml71(para)
